	<article class="post-625520 post type-post status-publish hentry category-industrials category-mergers-acquisitions tag-balfour-beatty-plc tag-building-construction tag-carillion-plc tag-great-britain tag-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures tag-parsons-brinckerhoff tag-stocks-and-bonds des-building-construction des-mergers-acquisitions-and-divestitures des-stocks-and-bonds org-balfour-beatty-plc org-carillion-plc org-parsons-brinckerhoff geo-great-britain news_keywords-balfour-beatty news_keywords-carillion news_keywords-construction news_keywords-great-britain news_keywords-mergers-and-acquistions news_keywords-parsons-brinckerhoff news_keywords-stocks-and-bonds" id="post-625520">
